  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA24">
<l>tāṉē taṉittōṉṟa ṟaṉṉaḷappoṉ ṟillātāṉ</l>
<l>ṟāṉē piṟarkaṭkun taṟṟōṉṟa ṟāṉē</l>
<l>yiḷaikkiṟpār kīḻmēlā mīṇṭa maippāṉāṉā</l>
<l>laḷakkiṟpār pāriṉmē lār.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He, he is a unique appearance. One without anything of his measure</l>
<l>is he. Also for others is his appearance. He,</l>
<l>without fatigue he further ordains what is below and above earth. Therefore,</l>
<l>who on earth can measure [him]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
